de.htwg_konstanz.ebus.framework.wholesaler.api.bo
Interface IBOUser

All Known Implementing Classes:
BOBaseUser, BOUserCustomer, BOUserInternal, BOUserSupplier
public interface IBOUser

The interface IBOUser represents the common attributes for all user entities.

To simplify the implementation and handling of the different user types (internal, customer and supplier) the framework provides a base class called BOBaseUser. This base class implements the IBOUser Interface and is defined as abstract, so you can't instantiate them. To work with user entities use the derived classes "BOUserInternal", "BOUserSupplier" and "BOUserCustomer" instead.
